# PODS :::::
- in the kubernetes pod is a smallest compute unit in that your container is running.
- pod is responsible for provide storage, security, contexts and network etc. for container. 
- kubernetes run every container and maintain using pod 
- pods is used for run application in kubernetes. 
- pod support one single container or multiple container (side-carcontainer, init container etc.)


# namespace :::: 
- in kubernetes namespace provide a logical space to segreate your enviornments 
- in kubernetes all services running in namespace
- default namespace is used if you not provide any namespace
- kube-system namespace is used manage kubenrentes key services. 

